ADAM KOCH: Pretty
bacon-friendly

00:05:46.420 --> 00:05:47.740
color scheme, actually.

00:05:47.740 --> 00:05:50.870
ROMAN NURIK: Yeah, a very
bacon-oriented reading

00:05:50.870 --> 00:05:51.150
experience.

