NICK BUTCHER: Yeah.

00:06:00.200 --> 00:06:03.390
ROMAN NURIK: So links and other
things throughout are

00:06:03.390 --> 00:06:07.650
accented with this orange,
so that's the next step.

00:06:07.650 --> 00:06:08.250
And then--

00:06:08.250 --> 00:06:09.430
ADAM KOCH: Yeah, and then
I guess from a developer

00:06:09.430 --> 00:06:10.610
standpoint--

00:06:10.610 --> 00:06:13.240
I think actually, Nick, you had
