00:18:03.446 --> 00:18:03.840
ROMAN NURIK: Yeah.

00:18:03.840 --> 00:18:04.990
Pretty terrible overall.

00:18:04.990 --> 00:18:06.063
If this is your tablet
experience,

00:18:06.063 --> 00:18:07.370
