00:18:17.190 --> 00:18:19.100
those tricks of spacing and
everything and see what that

00:18:19.100 --> 00:18:20.680
would that look like
on the tablet.

00:18:20.680 --> 00:18:23.570
It's much better, but still not
great, because you still

