the detail into a

00:18:51.170 --> 00:18:52.820
single two-pane UI.

00:18:52.820 --> 00:18:54.130
And this is fairly
straightforward.

00:18:57.090 --> 00:18:59.650
In Eclipse, you can do File,
New, Master Detail Flow to get

00:18:59.650 --> 00:19:02.910
you the basics for this,
