00:19:02.910 --> 00:19:04.585
articles you can read.

00:19:04.585 --> 00:19:06.910
ADAM KOCH: Yeah,
developers.Android.com/training

00:19:06.910 --> 00:19:09.500
has two really good training
classes on that.

00:19:09.500 --> 00:19:09.850
ROMAN NURIK: Yeah.

00:19:09.850 --> 00:19:12.490
So it's fairly straightforward
to do it these days.

00:19:12.490 --> 00:19:14.380
There's a lot of prewritten
code for you.

00:19:14.380 --> 00:19:17.700
It is fairly complex code if
