This is just the standard and
what we would recommend for

00:20:30.590 --> 00:20:33.050
looking at different sizes.

00:20:33.050 --> 00:20:34.020
NICK BUTCHER: And you
can provide multiple

00:20:34.020 --> 00:20:34.720
switchpoints, right?

