And actually, one that we don't
often talk about is

00:20:43.670 --> 00:20:44.790
small devices.

00:20:44.790 --> 00:20:47.510
So devices that have really
small screens, you may want to

00:20:47.510 --> 00:20:49.900
tweak things even further
there, maybe even start

00:20:49.900 --> 00:20:54.580
compressing information into
separate navigable sections.

00:20:54.580 --> 00:20:57.510
If your user base is on small
devices, then again, that's

00:20:57.510 --> 00:21:01.360
something that you want to do
using something like sw300 or

00:21:01.360 --> 00:21:07.680
200dp, or values-small,
for example.

00:21:07.680 --> 00:21:10.210
So let's actually look at some
of the metrics here, take a

00:21:10.210 --> 00:21:12.070
quick sidebar.

