If you're not using something
as large as 80 or 64dp for

00:21:41.110 --> 00:21:44.690
margins on a tablet, then you
probably should be, since you

00:21:44.690 --> 00:21:48.280
really want a lot of space so
that the eye can comfortably

00:21:48.280 --> 00:21:50.100
read the content.

