00:22:58.290 --> 00:23:00.905
expanded version actually
has that photo.

00:23:00.905 --> 00:23:03.100
Lets you maybe share
the article.

00:23:03.100 --> 00:23:05.480
And this is all very easy
to do from a developer

00:23:05.480 --> 00:23:06.440
standpoint.

00:23:06.440 --> 00:23:08.570
ADAM KOCH: There's a class
called NotificationCompat,

00:23:08.570 --> 00:23:10.940
which I think we've mentioned
before, that allows you to

00:23:10.940 --> 00:23:13.210
build these richer notifications
from newer

00:23:13.210 --> 00:23:14.940
platform versions, but
remains backward

00:23:14.940 --> 00:23:18.010
compatible with older versions.

00:23:18.010 --> 00:23:19.480
Definitely good to use.

00:23:19.480 --> 00:23:22.330
ROMAN NURIK: Yeah, super
trivial, I'd say, to use.

00:23:22.330 --> 00:23:23.980
It's only couple
lines of code.

